data.description: Welcome to this charming brick home located in Penn Hills. This lovely property offers 3 bedrooms, 1 bath, and hardwood floors. Outside, the property boasts a good-sized yard and covered back patio, providing ample space for outdoor activities, gardening, or simply enjoying the fresh air.  Additionally, the home offers close proximity to the nearby Duff Community Park. Located in the heart of Penn Hills, this home provides a wonderful opportunity to enjoy the best of suburban living while still being within easy reach of the city's amenities and attractions.  Don't miss out on the chance to make this delightful home your own. Schedule a showing today!
